    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:0",
      "text": "Starting a Batch Render（启动 Batch Render）",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:1",
      "text": "Batch renders 的启动位置是",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:2",
      "text": "RenderMan Menu 菜单入口",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:3",
      "text": "。Maya 的 Batch Render menu entry 也可使用。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:4",
      "text": "Stopping a Batch Render（停止 Batch Render）",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:5",
      "text": "Batch renders 可以在 Local Queue 或 Tractor 中 delete 或 pause。右键点击列表中的 job 可打开 menu。",
      "ascii_letters": 47,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:6",
      "text": "Render Settings",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:7",
      "text": "Render Settings window 中的 settings 会用于 batch renders。尤其是 Frame Range 和 Renderable Cameras 会在 Common tab 下指定。对于 preview renders，则改用 current frame 或 active camera。",
      "ascii_letters": 114,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:8",
      "text": "Batch Queuing（批量渲染队列）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:9",
      "text": "Batch renders 总会 spool 到 LocalQueue（default）或",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:12",
      "text": "Batch queuing preferences（批量队列首选项）",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:13",
      "text": "可在 Maya Preferences window 中找到；选择 Batch Render menu item 的 option box 时会打开该 window。请注意，spool style 定义是先 export 到 RIB files 再 render，还是直接通过 Maya Batch render。",
      "ascii_letters": 100,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:14",
      "text": "Output Locations（输出位置）",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:15",
      "text": "默认情况下，我们使用 Mayabatch 来 render 已保存的 Maya scene file。Maya 会从 memory 渲染，类似于从 UI 发起的 preview render，不进行 intermediate RIB export。",
      "ascii_letters": 74,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:16",
      "text": "启动 batch render 时，RIB files 和 textures 会存储在 disk 上，renderer 会读取这些内容。它们会存储在一个基于 scene name、并追加 time stamp 的 directory 中。preferences 里的 Batch Context setting 用于指定这个 time stamp，其变量名为 $JOBDATETIME。这可以避免多个 simultaneous jobs 尝试 overwrite files。",
      "ascii_letters": 146,
      "cjk_chars": 53
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:17",
      "text": "Output locations 在 RenderMan for Maya 的",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:18",
      "text": "Workspace",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:20",
      "text": "Local Queue",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:21",
      "text": "LocalQueue 用于运行 render jobs 的 local queue。它会读取",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:22",
      "text": "job scripts 作业脚本文件",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:23",
      "text": "这些 scripts 由 RenderMan for Maya 生成，然后运行 scripts 中的 commands，在 local computer 上 render 你的 scene。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:24",
      "text": "render job 加载到 LocalQueue 后，你应能在",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:29",
      "text": "Checkpointing（检查点保存功能）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:31",
      "text": "checkpointing 检查点功能",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:32",
      "text": "会为 batch renders 启用。Images 每五分钟更新到 disk。checkpoint interval 可在",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:33",
      "text": "batch preferences 批量首选项",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:34",
      "text": "中配置。Incremental mode 默认启用，位于 Render Settings 的 Sampling tab 下。这是 checkpointing 正常工作所必需的。",
      "ascii_letters": 53,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:35",
      "text": "Maya Batch Rendering from the Command Line（从命令行进行 Maya Batch Rendering）",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:36",
      "text": "你也可以使用 additional flags：-rl（render layer）、-crop、-preRender、-postRender、-preLayer、-postLayer、-preFrame、-postFrame、-jobid",
      "ascii_letters": 90,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:38",
      "text": "Render -r renderman sceneFile",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:40",
      "text": "Render -r renderman -rib sceneFile",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:42",
      "text": "Render -r renderman -h",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:43",
      "text": "如果收到类似以下 warning，需要将 RenderMan for Maya installation 中的 rmanRenderer.xml 和 ribRenderer.xml 放到 Maya 能找到的位置。",
      "ascii_letters": 68,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:44",
      "text": "警告消息示例：Cannot open renderer description file \"rendermanRenderer.xml\"",
      "ascii_letters": 53,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:45",
      "text": "你可以从 RenderMan for Maya installation 复制这些 files，",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:46",
      "text": "eg. C:/Program Files/Pixar/RenderManForMaya-22.0/etc/rendermanRenderer.xml",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:47",
      "text": "放入 Maya installation 中 Maya 查找这些 files 的 directory，",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:48",
      "text": "eg. C:/Program Files/Autodesk/Maya2018/bin/rendererDesc/",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:49",
      "text": "或者，你可以设置名为 MAYA_RENDER_DESC_PATH 的 Maya environment variable，以便找到 rmanRenderer.xml 和 ribRenderer.xml。",
      "ascii_letters": 70,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:50",
      "text": "Prman Rendering from the Command Line (Advanced)（从命令行进行 Prman 渲染，高级）",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:53",
      "text": "render 时，RenderMan for Maya 会生成 RIB files，然后针对这些 rib files 启动 prman（executable）。不过，你可能已经有 disk 上的 RIB files，只想对它们运行 prman。",
      "ascii_letters": 70,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:54",
      "text": "Job Structure（作业结构说明）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:55",
      "text": "RenderMan for Maya 生成的 RIB files 位于 maya project 内。例如：",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:56",
      "text": "<maya_project>/renderman/myscene/rib/",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:57",
      "text": "RIB files 会按每个 frame 组织到 subdirectories 中，如 0001、0002、0003。另有一个名为 \"job\" 的 subdirectory，用于 static objects 的 caches，以及不需要每帧执行的 processing commands，例如 converting textures 和 cleanup。",
      "ascii_letters": 104,
      "cjk_chars": 32
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:58",
      "text": "下面是一个 three frame job 通常会执行的 commands 示例。请注意，这里使用 -cwd arg 将 maya project 指定为 prman 运行时的 current working directory。rib file 的 project relative path 作为 command 的最后一个 argument 提供。Rib files 默认包含 project relative paths。",
      "ascii_letters": 135,
      "cjk_chars": 42
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:59",
      "text": "prman -t:0 -cwd C:/Users/user/Documents/maya/projects/default/ renderman/test_0725120019/rib/job/job.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 72,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:60",
      "text": "prman -t:0 -cwd C:/Users/user/Documents/maya/projects/default/ renderman/test_0725120019/rib/0001/0001.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:61",
      "text": "prman -t:0 -cwd C:/Users/user/Documents/maya/projects/default/ renderman/test_0725120019/rib/0002/0002.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:62",
      "text": "prman -t:0 -cwd C:/Users/user/Documents/maya/projects/default/ renderman/test_0725120019/rib/0003/0003.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:63",
      "text": "prman -t:0 -cwd C:/Users/user/Documents/maya/projects/default/ renderman/test_0725120019/rib/job/post.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 73,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:64",
      "text": "每个 frame rib file（如 0001.rib）都会引用位于同一 directory 中的其他 rib files，这些 files 对应于该 frame 中 active 的每个 camera 或 render layer。下面是 frame directory 中典型内容的示例：",
      "ascii_letters": 79,
      "cjk_chars": 37
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:65",
      "text": "renderman/test_0725120019/rib/0001:",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:67",
      "text": "perspShape_Final.0001.rib",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:68",
      "text": "perspShape_Final.0001.rlf",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:69",
      "text": "perspShape_Final.0001.xml",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:70",
      "text": "名为 0001.rib 的 file 是该 frame 的 \"driver\" RIB file。它会引用该 frame 中每个 pass（用于不同 cameras 或 render layers）的 RIB files。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:71",
      "text": "directory 中有一些 files 不是 RIB files。它们是什么？",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:72",
      "text": "用户制作的 RLF files（分配给 GPU archives）包含 material 和 binding information。Materials 会在 render time 由 RIF 注入到 RIB file 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 74,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "62a48f5da8:73",
      "text": "XML file 会在 rendering 期间生成。它包含关于 render 的 diagnostic information。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    }
  ],
